ed="T" n="0782c19"/><persName key="A009348">釋元安</persName>，俗姓<name>淡</name>，<placeName key="PL000000042995">鳳翔<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>遊麟</sic><corr>麟游</corr></choice></placeName>人也<ptr target="#n1662"/>。丱年於<placeName key="PL000000042867"><anchor xml:id="beg0782sgsz24"/>岐<anchor xml:id="end0782sgsz24"/>陽<lb
ed="T" n="0782c20"/>懷恩寺</placeName>從兄<persName key="A010615">祐<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>出家。唯經與論，無不<lb
ed="T" n="0782c21"/>窮<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>核</sic><corr>該</corr></choice><ptr target="#n1663"/>。乃問道<persName key="A010616">翠微</persName>，次<persName key="A003627">臨濟</persName>，各飡法味，<anchor xml:id="beg0782sgsz28"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>不</sic><corr>若</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0782sgsz28"/>飫<lb
ed="T" n="0782c22"/>香積之盂也。斵彫復朴<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1616"/>，逍遙自如。聞<persName key="A003669">夾山</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0782c23"/>道盛德至，造<placeName key="PL000000029560">澧陽</placeName>當稽問轇轕<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1617"/>，又增明淨。<lb
ed="T" n="0782c24"/>後開<placeName key="PL000000029554">樂普山</placeName>，尋居<placeName key="PL000000029555">蘇溪</placeName>，答詶請益，多偶句華<lb
ed="T" n="0782c25"/>美，為四海傳焉。以<persName key="A003875">昭宗</persName><date from-iso="+0899-01-20" key="j20494332049461" to-iso="+0899-02-17"><name>光化</name>元年戊午十二<lb
ed="T" n="0782c26"/>月</date><ptr target="#n1664"/>遷滅，享壽六十五，法臘四十六矣。臨終<lb
ed="T" n="0782c27"/>告眾，頗多警策辭句云。</p>
